                                                            
                                                                QUARTZ
https://www.opencodez.com/java/quartz-scheduler-with-spring-boot.htm
It is a job scheduling library. A job which needs to be scheduled at some particular time.

Components of Quartz

1) JOB             any task which needs to be performed.
2) TRIGGER         A stored program which will be fired at a given time.
                   1) Simple trigger - fired only once
                   2) Cron trigger   - fired at every intervals
3) SCHEDULER       Role of a scheduler is to schedule a job when a trigger is occured.
